  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "雷明顿 MSR .300 WM 栓动式狙击步枪",
      "en": "Remington MSR .300 WM bolt-action sniper rifle"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "MSR",
      "en": "MSR"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "模块化狙击步枪（Modular Sniper Rifle，简称MSR）是由雷明顿公司为美国陆军研发生产的一款栓动狙击步枪。该枪于2009年推出，旨在满足美国陆军及特种作战司令部（USSOCOM）对精密狙击步枪的特定需求。MSR最初在精密狙击步枪（PSR）竞标中胜出，美军将其命名为雷明顿Mk21精密狙击步枪。但2018年军方认定Mk21不符合特种作战司令部的要求，遂重启招标程序，最终于2019年选定巴雷特MRAD步枪作为Mk22先进狙击步枪解决方案。",
      "en": "The Modular Sniper Rifle, or MSR, is a bolt-action sniper rifle developed and produced by Remington Arms for the United States Army. It was introduced in 2009, and was designed to meet specific United States Army and USSOCOM Precision Sniper Rifle requirements. The MSR initially won the PSR competition, and was called the Remington Mk 21 Precision Sniper Rifle in U.S. military service. However, it was then decided that the Mk 21 did not conform to SOCOM requirements at the time in 2018, and the program was re-competed with the Barrett MRAD selected in 2019 as the Mk 22 Advanced Sniper Rifle solution."
    },
